data.description: Escape to a unique living experience with this 5 bed, 4.5 bath home. Nestled on a quarter-acre, relax in the serenity of a flat, private, tree-lined backyard-perfect for evenings on the elevated deck or lounging on the covered patio. Elegance awaits inside as abundant natural light dances across LVP floors throughout. The unique & flexible layout has a loft, flex room, & can host guests in the private main level suite. Cozy up in the living room, graced with a chic tile fireplace, flowing seamlessly into a chef's dream kitchen. The stunning sunroom is your sanctuary of southern sunshine flowing through the home. A high-ceilinged, unfinished, walkout basement holds endless potential. Visit today & unlock the authentic life you've envisioned!
